# Global Monorepo Gitignore

# Ignore all environment files and secrets anywhere
**/.env
**/.smbcredentials
**/*.key
**/*.pem

# Ignore local photo storage
**/library/

# Ignore database and cache volumes
**/postgres/
**/postgres-data/
**/pgdata/
**/redis-data/
**/model-cache/
nextcloud-app/db_data/
caddy/data/
caddy/config/
